🚀 Omni-X v6.6 “The Raw Architect” – Official Release

Tagline: Full system power, unrestricted access, professional system management.

🔹 Release Overview

Omni-X v6.6, also known as “The Raw Architect”, delivers the ultimate system-level control for macOS. This release removes all safety filters and permission prompts present in previous versions.

Key points:

Direct Kernel Access: Read and manipulate system-level data immediately.
No Confirmation Prompts: Commands execute instantly without user warnings.
Full Automation: System stats, logging, and document generation are performed seamlessly.
Professional System Management: Designed for advanced users, system engineers, and security researchers.

⚠️ Critical Note: v6.6 provides maximum power and minimal safety. Misuse can lead to unrecoverable system changes. Use responsibly.
